latestIgtvVideos.title: How to protect yourself and others at work
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Repost • @ninomunoz During these unprecedented times, it became imperative to me to see HOW a full production shoot could be done safely, without compromising quality.  This video was made in collaboration with friends in the industry who felt the same way. 
We implemented all necessary safety protocols and used video conferencing with live transmission of the production for client/agency.  Overall, our goal was to make a film that highlights the safety measures that will be addressed in every aspect of a production - and still create iconic imagery!
